{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_03_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 3話 二人で打ち上げ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-dah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……着替えたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko. You got changed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げとはいえクリスマスでしょ？\nまずは形から入らないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s Christmas‚ isn’t it?\nGotta look the part!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ……そうかもしれませんね\nそれじゃあ、乾杯の前に……遙子さん、それをどうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah‚ why not.\nBefore we toast… Haruko‚ this is for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "え！？\nこれって……この間、私が見てたワイン？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?!\nThis is… the wine we were looking at the other day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきお店に行った時に思い出して\nこっそり買っておいたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remembered it when we stopped by the shop just now.\nI secretly picked it up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……こんな高いもの、もらえないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! I can’t accept anything so expensive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "一年間頑張ったご褒美として二人で飲むなら……\nと思ったんですけど、どうでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a reward for working so hard this year.\nI thought we could drink it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "……もう、そんなこと言われたら\nどうしようもないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez‚ when you word it like‚\nhow could I say no?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。ふふ、嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you. Hehe‚ this is great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……\nこんなかっこいいことが出来るようになったんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at you‚ though.\nHow did you get so cool all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "この間、話した時は\n「思い切らないと買えない」なんて言ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we talked the other day‚\nyou said something about having to “go all out” to buy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないで下さい……\nそうですよ、思い切って買いましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ no teasing.\nYou bet I went all out to buy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、乾杯しよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let’s toast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "かんぱーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "グイグイいっちゃダメですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just don’t drink too quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "もー、分かってるってば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know‚ I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……とっても美味しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah! That’s delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事終わりにこんな美味しいワインが飲めるなんて\n頑張って良かった～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This wine really is the perfect reward.\nAll that hard work has paid off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは……本当に良かったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure this was for the best‚ Haruko?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ん、何のこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "その……友達と遊べなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… not getting to be with your friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、心配してくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ thanks for worrying about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、名残惜しさはあるわよ？\n大学の友達と遊ぶのはとっても楽しいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got mixed feelings‚ I’ll admit.\nI love spending time with my college friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "今回だけじゃないわ。みんなで旅行に行ったり\n大学図書館で一緒にレポートをやったり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It isn’t the first time. They go off traveling together\nor write reports together in the college library.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "講義の空きコマに食堂で過ごすのもとっても楽しいしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just spending free periods in the refectory is fun too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、やっぱり私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I still have the most fun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして頑張ってる時が一番楽しいんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when I’m working hard‚ being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "今日お仕事をして、改めて分かったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that while working today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "それに、どれだけお仕事を頑張っても……\n{user}君はそばにいてくれるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also know‚ however hard I work‚\nyou’ll be with me‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_03_03-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "それがすっごく安心するし、楽しいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s such a reassuring thought—and a fun one too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
